    <p>(Soundbite of conversation) </p>
    <p>Unidentified Child #4: Kind person, helpful. </p>
    <p>Mr. SCHRAM: Helpful, kind and helpful. Okay, I'm going to try to express who I am, as a kind and helpful person, on the violin. </p>
