    <p>President BARACK OBAMA: My principle focus, my number one focus, is going to be making sure that we are competitive, that we are growing, and we are creating jobs - not just now, but well into the future. And that's what is going to be the main topic of the State of the Union. </p>
    <p>HANSEN: The president in a YouTube video he released yesterday. </p>
    <p>Polls show more Americans approve of the job he's doing than in recent months. </p>
