    <p>TOTENBERG: Fifty years later, the center is celebrating that pivotal moment for arts in America. The project has been on the drawing board for five years under Michael Kaiser's direction.</p>
    <p>M: You can never be encyclopedic in a festival. So you start to think about highlights.</p>
