    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF "SONG OF THE BIRDS")</p>
    <p>TOTENBERG: The next morning, a photograph of the concert would be emblazoned across the front page of The New York Times. Kennedy Center president Kaiser was a boy then, but he remembers the excitement generated by that concert.</p>
